{"tid":2236571,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"Viutv 玩謝我阿婆（新旅遊節目） 28/9 (2)","createTime":"2020-10-09T14:35:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-09T15:52:18.000Z","uid":33798,"like":7,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"f50f225b65e8d844fd55203dd38b4890132681f7","tid":2236571,"uid":33798,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:35:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GsjwQE5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGsjwQE5.jpg&h=6c76cc9d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n《玩‧謝我阿婆》（英語：Travel with Grandma）是香港電視娛樂製作的一套旅遊節目，由陳柏宇、羅彩玲主持，於2020年9月28日在ViuTV首播。本節目由「王朝滴雞精」冠名贊助。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n歌手陳柏宇（Jason）昨日出席ViuTV節目《玩．謝我阿婆》記者會，他透露節目已是兩年前拍攝，當時與婆婆遊台南，今次並非首次婆孫去旅行，年幼時經常跟她返香港：「唔知點解細個好鍾意返香港，揀去邊我實揀香港。」問到日後待疫情好轉，會否出錢請婆婆去旅行？他竟然拒絕，指公公婆婆比他更有錢：「佢哋夠錢請自己，因為佢喺加拿大包糉包咗廿幾年，又開過食品廠，雖然利潤好細，但佢哋好勤力，依家退休賣咗畀人，不過仲有好幾個舖位收租，加上佢哋啲樓同子女又供好晒，我就話有排供啫！」"},{"pid":"120372d6837cbb53a7b8075fe832ec5194d6551a","tid":2236571,"uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"諗起Coco<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a026aa0c7a8382427dea85bfe4030e477210814","tid":2236571,"uid":92376,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:36:36.000Z","msg":"屌啦星 阿婆都搵把男仔聲配<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44c3765e194e71bdb9bd954500ef84ccaab09369","tid":2236571,"uid":313584,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"120372d6837cbb53a7b8075fe832ec5194d6551a","tid":2236571,"uid":34777,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-09T14:36:08.000Z","msg":"諗起Coco<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><im